4 Imagine my delight when I saw that the Nile is now open for breakfast! I am a huge fan of the hummus, lentil soup and spanakopita here, so I was excited to try out breakfast. I couldn't be more pleased :-) I am mostly vegan so when I asked whether they could prepare grilled veggies, potatoes and toast for breakfast, they didn't hesitate to accommodate. I was also very happy to learn that they will be rolling out a gluten free and vegan menu, score! I will certainly be back...and did I mention that the delicious hummus is now available at AJs?? Can't wait to tell all of my friends!
